All of amazing stuff AI can do right now.

Generate a tool after failing to find a good online tool

  • M4A to MP3 Converter

Generated a website based off code, a logo and a tagline as the input

  • https://beckon.run - Generated landing page for Beckon
  • https://anchor.host/the-age-of-personal-generated-applications/ - more details in this blog post

Generated a WordPress plugin to render html on the home page.

  • https://gemini.google.com/share/9bdf35440417

CaptainCore Helm v1 release - reimagining WordPress wp-admin as a single menu island.

  • https://github.com/CaptainCore/Helm

AI is really good at incrementally adding features as you need them. This very presentation view was added to Beckon with one prompt.

Anchor Hosting recent updates (with Google AI Studio)

  • Overhauled all WooCommerce/account related email notification with styled emails from Google Gemini: https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/1QM027FPSulP5hPQsCbgFdoSIa4KhPqKy
  • Revamped sites listing with proper support for environments and better UI like magic login more useable.
  • Revamped web based scripting into a web based terminal UI.

Everything AI is breaking.

AI killed Stackflow's traffic. Stackflow increases revenue thanks to AI licensing deals.

  • https://sherwood.news/tech/stack-overflow-forum-dead-thanks-ai-but-companys-still-kicking-ai/

Linus Torvalds uses AI to code

  • https://github.com/torvalds/AudioNoise/commit/93a72563cba609a414297b558cb46ddd3ce9d6b5

Open source CSS framework Tailwind at an all time high but also revenue at all time low. Owner of Tailwind lays off 75% of staff.

  • https://x.com/adamwathan/status/2008909129591443925

What will be possible in the near future?

Scaling long-running autonomous coding - Jan 14, 2026 by Wilson Lin

  • https://cursor.com/blog/scaling-agents - research page
  • https://github.com/wilsonzlin/fastrender - generated code

What's possible in the future?

  • Large project rewritten in new languages?
  • Individual business owners running whole fleets of AI agents for all roles of a company?

Takeways

  • What used to take 2 - 3 hours I've easily generated in 1 minute with Google Gemini thinking. Not a one time happening. It keeps happening the more I use AI.
  • AI is a massive productive boast for developers right now.
  • Think bigger, have more thoughts and write more. Writing translates thoughts into pseudo code which is good enough to actually make things.
  • Use more AI tokens, experiment and try new things.
  • Have AI build more tools or plugins to help you.
